        <div id="main__content" class="main__content">
            <p id="main__text" class="main__text">The web applications which compose this website were written to be presented as our group's final project for The Pennsylvania State University's Math 468 course on coding theory and information theory.  The project is fully open-source (<a href="https://github.com/whatsacomputertho/math468-final-project">see the repository here</a>) and contribution is encouraged.  Please email Ethan Balcik (emb71@psu.edu) with any questions.</p>
